You're right, I only addressed horizontal centering. Here's proper centering in both directions:

```css
.centered {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  min-height: 100vh;
}
```

Or with CSS Grid:

```css
.centered {
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
  min-height: 100vh;
}
